ages" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Red cabbage" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Braised cabbage" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Slow-cooked red cabbage" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Red cabbage with spices" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Christmas trimmings" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Side dishes" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Red wine vinegar" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Easy" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Vegetarian" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Christmas" /><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Freezable" /></div></div><div class="recipe-header__description" itemprop="description"><div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden method__content"><div class="field-items"><div class="field-item even">This colourful dish will complement any
